00:39:14.875 --> 00:39:19.004
-Lim Hyeon-jun!
-Lim Hyeon-jun!

00:39:22.465 --> 00:39:23.592
I'll have a drink.

00:39:36.813 --> 00:39:37.731
I hope…

00:39:38.899 --> 00:39:42.569
we never see each other again,
you little shit!

00:39:43.695 --> 00:39:46.740
And the Best Actor award
goes to Lim Hyeon-jun

00:39:46.823 --> 00:39:48.909
from Good Detective Kang Pil-gu.

00:39:48.992 --> 00:39:52.329
We'll now hear
Mr. Lim Hyeon-jun's acceptance speech.

00:39:55.498 --> 00:39:59.044
By some miracle,
I've been given a second chance…

00:40:00.754 --> 00:40:02.005
and I won't let it slip away.

00:40:03.548 --> 00:40:04.674
From now on,

00:40:05.425 --> 00:40:08.470
I hope to act for a long time
alongside all of you…

00:40:12.849 --> 00:40:16.478
in a way that will be remembered.

